Simulate streaming data into Aurora tables.

Usage:
  stream
      Simulate the default scenario (profile).

  stream --scenario <name>
      Simulate a specific scenario with controlled behavior.

Flags:
  --scenario       Name of the scenario to simulate: profile, review
                   If omitted, the default 'profile' scenario will be executed.
  --rps            Records per second per parallel stream (default: 10)
  --duration       Total duration of simulation, e.g., 30s, 2m (default: 30s)
  --parallel       Number of goroutines per scenario (default: 1)
  --quality        Data quality level: high (default), medium, low

Examples:
  stream
  stream --scenario profile --rps 50 --duration 2m
  stream --scenario review --quality low --parallel 3
